; The average maximum temperature is a measure of the average highest temperature recorded over a period of time; 

; The wind direction at 3 PM is a key factor in determining weather patterns; 

; Estimated rainfall risk for the next day is a forecast of the likelihood of rain based on current weather conditions.

sql:
SELECT date 
FROM weather_data 
WHERE max_temp = (SELECT MAX(max_temp) FROM weather_data);
